{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, to-- we found out that these children were taken away on the orders of the Gestapo and sent to Sachsenhausen, which we knew to be a concentration camp, to be sent from there to other places and wherever.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've got no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The point was, what we learned from that was that, hey, they're not going home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're not going to visit their uncles and all that sort of thing, that there is a scheme in this whole situation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we faced him, and he finally [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] owned up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, there is, but please don't talk about it, because the fact is, as upset he is about it, there's nothing he can do about it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was his point of view.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we talked about it and we said, OK, if we're going to sit here and, you know, we're getting close to 14th-- and it didn't take place exactly on the 14th.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was around about that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it could be two months later, it could be at the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We decided we're going to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it happens even today that kids run away, so there were-- under those circumstances.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The fact was, I had been through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew what happened to my father, that he had to disappear, and I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My time's come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've got to make an effort.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was either-- what can happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I get caught, I get sent to camp with its consequences of possible-- we didn't know at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew there were camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that it wasn't a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't a-- a place where you go for [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Holiday camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Holiday camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
